data.description: Over 1300 square feet of main floor living in this spacious and open 3 bed, 1 bath ranch home.  It doesn't get any better than this convenient Portage location!  The large living room opens to the updated kitchen and spacious dining room and bonus snack bar. Perfect for entertaining!  The backyard is mostly fenced with brand new concrete patio for your outdoor parties.  Spacious laundry space conveniently located on the main floor.  Roof new in 2016.  Schedule your showing today!
